    <Entry>
      <ID>7</ID>
      <DefaultText>[The First enters, yells at you for a bit about plot-interesting information, then leaves.

Shortly after she leaves, the tower comes under attack by Oorgolian soldiers. The means to fend them off turns out to be similar to how you opened the portal, but your choices there affect what you can do here.]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>8</ID>
      <DefaultText>[Fend off the attack.]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>9</ID>
