      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>10</ID>
      <DefaultText>[Dick around some more.]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>11</ID>
      <DefaultText>[It is extremely effective! For solving the Mere, you get some DP and other rewards, push back the Sorrow a bit, trigger some cool Mere-related reactivity for later in the world, and learn valuable lessons about love and friendship.]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>12</ID>
      <DefaultText>[You activate some of the defenses, fighting off some of the soldiers, but eventually they overcome your defenses. You don't solve the Mere, but you get some cool Mere-related reactivity for later in the world and learn valuable lessons about love and friendship.]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>13</ID>
      <DefaultText>[You succeed at dicking around. The attack destroys Endira, but what do you care? You're just using his body to dick around. You get some cool Mere-related reactivity for later in the game, but you missed out on the lessons about love and friendship.]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
